- `.env` ŌĆö local defaults, gitignored
- `.env.local` ŌĆö personal local overrides, gitignored
- `.env.example` ŌĆö committed template
- **prod** ŌĆö no file; set vars in the deployment platform / a secrets manager (AWS Secrets Manager, Doppler, Vault) for sensitive values

